title: About
description: My name is Mike. I am an undergraduate at Macquarie University studying a Bachelor of Information Technology, majoring in Software Technology.

title: Hello, Blog!
description: For my first blog post it seemed fitting to pay homage to almost everyone's first programming project Hello, World! - continuing on from this theme, we will be taking a look at Hello, World! implemented in a few languages. Namely C, Java, Python, Scala, and Rust.
